item.title: Netheravon 25. September 2009
item.description: Back here again, desperately trying to find an FS-1 coach to get my FS-1 license done. Only did one jump today as I developed one very nasty headache and it seems this is one of the rare times I didn’t bring any painkillers along. Oh, what fun ;-) Beside that the Friday night jumps will commence soon, preparations are under way as I speak (I mean write). KPICASA_GALLERY(Netheravon)
